       <h1 class="clear">
        Prospective Students
       </h1>
       <p>
        RSRG is actively recruiting both graduate students and postdocs in the smart grid area.  We are looking for exceptional students who are interested in a combination of real system design and theoretical analysis.
       </p>
       <ul class="sidemenu">
        <li>
         <a href="http://www.gradoffice.caltech.edu/">
          <b>
           Prospective Grads
          </b>
          <br/>
          Apply through the graduate studies office. RSRG will consider applicants to EE, CS, or ACM.  Please refrain from sending personal emails to faculty in the group.  Instead mention your interest in RSRG in your statement.
         </a>
        </li>
        <li>
         <a href="http://www.ist.caltech.edu/joinus/positions.html#postdoc">
          <b>
           Prospective postdocs
          </b>
          <br/>
          RSRG typically has 2-4 postdocs at any point in time.  Applications should be submitted through the CMI program, but please also contact the faculty within the group directly to discuss opportunities.
         </a>
        </li>
       </ul>
      </div>
